blog.name: k-eke
blog.title: kéké
blog.description: Bonjour ! Je m'appelle Kévin Gemin et je vous souhaite la bienvenue sur mon blog. Animations principalement ^^ J'ai obtenu mon diplôme de dessinateur praticien à l'Ecole Emile Cohl. facebook pour des dessins, animations en cours et poser vos questions... Twitter Pour chatter un peu ! To chat with me! Youtube Pour mes vidéos ! For my videos! Deviantart Pour des animations traditionnelles For traditional animations Patreon Pour me soutenir ! To support me ! Hello everybody and welcome to my Tumblr, there I share mostly all of my animations, I love 2D animation a lot and do it mostly with my life. As for my program, I draw on my DSi (Yes!) and my 3DS !!! With a program called Flipnote Studio! It's amazing for me to be able to create diverse ideas and animations from a DSi and being able to share all of them with you. No matter what you use to create, if you really love what you do, you will be able to do your best and share it with the world. Remember that the talent is on you, not on what you use with your body :) You can try to listen to a song while looking through my blog, it can be funny ^^ Also you can share some gifs if you want but always Link my blog please ! Thanks !! No need to tell you that I love pigeons :) !
